  <Section title="Poverty Scorcher" emoji="💸">
    <p>
      This set does <b>not require any skills</b> on your Gogma weapon, it works right out of the box.
      Because of this restriction, we can't run Bloodlust, so the focus is on getting <b
        >Lord's Soul</b
      > and <b>Scorcher</b> instead.
    </p>

    <p>
      We use 2 AT Jin Dahaad pieces to unlock <b>Binding Counter</b>, and the new AT Arkveld legs to
      activate Lord's Soul. As an easy optional upgrade, rolling for <b>Arkveld's Hunger</b> on your
      weapon gives you some nice healing since you're already running the legs anyway.
    </p>

