  <Section title="Comfy Healing" emoji="❤️‍🩹">
    <p>
      Thanks to AT Arkveld armor, we actually have a kinda competitive comfy healing set again. We
      run double AT and double Numinous pieces to unlock both,
      <b>Arkveld's Hunger</b> and <b>Zoh Shia's Pulse</b>. The first heals you when you attack,
      while the second is a passive regen effect. Both skills have diminishing returns, which is why
      we get <b>both</b> but only at level 1.
    </p>

    <p>
      With the new Nadia armor, we are actually able to still fit <b>Gore Magala's</b> set bonus, so
      we're not really missing out too much on damage, except for not having Scorcher.
    </p>

